Vesalius is an open source tool that combines honeypot
technology with deep monitoring and data analysis thus
turning it into a defensive intelligence tool.

1. Vesalius develops its own presense based on it's environment.
It will adapt its look and feel to legitimate sources in it's 
direct vincinity. As it learns more about its surroundings, it 
will blend into the infrastructure more.

2. Vesalius acts as an high interaction honeypot. The ultimate
goal is to keep the attacker around for as long as it can and
at the same time provide it with unique, tainted data and flags.
This will enable the user to track attackers over several who:q

